#compdef toga2
# Documentation: https://manpages.debian.org/bookworm/toga2/toga2.6.en.html
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-16
# Verified: Debian bookworm toga2(6) manpage. Toga II is a UCI engine
# driven entirely by UCI commands on stdin; no CLI flag table.
